    <h1>Hi there, </h1>
    <p>here you can see one of the use case applications of the V-MANIP Project. This application demonstrates how comparison between 2D data such as model or satellite data can be achieved through a 2D Difference Image</p>
    <p>This tutorial banner will present to you the available functionality and tools needed to visualize and compare the data.</p>
    <p>We will go through the available tools and visualizations as a tutorial which can be scrolled through. </p>
    <p>Under the parent <a href="http://demo.v-manip.eox.at/validation/">website</a> you can find the the different use case Apps, where again a banner like this will walk you through the steps for different tools. We recommend you to have a look at them too.</p>
    <p>You can always close this banner and play around with the system to get acquanted to it.</p>
