    <h2>Tools</h2>
    <p>To use the difference process an additional area selection is necessary. This can be done in with the bounding box tool in the Tools pane.</p>
    <p>We opened it automatically for you but as the Layer Widget you can open and close the Tool Widget by clicking on the Tools button with the icon <i class="fa fa-fw fa-wrench"></i>.</p>
    <p>In the next step we will create a bounding box selection for you.</p>
</section>
